Class WidgetSavedState

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.ui.widget.WidgetSavedState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseProgressBar.SavedState, CalendarView.SavedState, CircularNumberPicker.SavedState, CollectionSavedState, EditLayout.SavedState, InputLayout.SavedState, LinearProgressBar.SavedState, MonthView.SavedState, SearchView.SavedState, SeekBarWidget.SavedState, SpinnerLayout.SavedState

    public abstract class WidgetSavedState
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    Saved state implementation like View.BaseSavedState that should be used by all custom widgets from the UI library and also for theirs derivatives.
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
